libshout: libshout (Streaming Shoutcast Library)
libshout:
libshout: libshout is used by audio players to access streaming media servers. 
libshout: It supports Ogg Vorbis and MP3 audio streams, and can be used to create 
libshout: an Internet radio station or a privately running jukebox and many things 
libshout: in between. It is very versatile in that new formats can be added 
libshout: relatively easily and supports open standards for communication and 
libshout: interaction.
libshout:
libshout: libshout is available from http://icecast.org
libshout:
